// Fork from polygons

To "play" build tests and run box:

$ make tests
$ ./build/box


After pressing s (for start), a cube falls in the direction
indicated by the user. Default's is down (in y's axis), and can be
changed by pressing x, y, z, X, Y, Z.

Also, projection plane can be moves presing f and b (this must
change), by rotating the vector normal to it.


